data.eml:eml: Catalogus hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus. Volumen VII: Formicidae (Heterogyna).

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Dalla Torre, C. G. de (1893): Catalogus hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus. Volumen VII: Formicidae (Heterogyna). Catalogus hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus 7: 1-289, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.11547
